title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 21, ch. XVIII - Delaware River Basin Commission
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 21, ch. XVIII - Delaware River Basin Commission

State Regulations

Subchapter A - Rules Of Practice And Procedure (Part 830 to 839)

Subchapter B - Water Quality Regulations (Part 850 to 861)

Subchapter C - Flood Plain Regulations (Part 870 to 874)

Subchapter D - Water Supply Charges (Part 880 to 884)

Subchapter E - Water Code (Part 890)

Subchapter F - Miscellaneous (Part 895)

Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 21, ch. XVIII
Chapter XVIII was reorganized to better represent the text of
the Delaware River Basin Commission's rules and republished with the March 1993
supplement to the NYCRR. The individual historical notes in each section do not
indicate this action. State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
